    public abstract class ModelCheckerImpl
extends org.eclipse.emf.ecore.impl.MinimalEObjectImpl.Container
implements ModelChecker
    An implementation of the model object 'Model Checker'.

    This class is intended to be used in two possible ways:

    1. verify a single VerificationUnit and return a VerificationResult
    2. verifiy of a collection of VerificationUnits and collect all results in a ResultsCollection.
    Typical use: 

     Resource r = ...;
 Model m1 = ...;
 Specification s1 = ...;
 Viewpoint v1 = ...;
 Component c1 = ...;
 VerificationUnit vc1 = VerifiersFactory.eINSTANCE.createVerificationUnit();
 vc1.setModel(m1);
 vc1.setSpecification(s1);
 vc1.setViewpoint(v1);
 vc1.setComponetn(c1);
 // possibly more VerificationUnits
 ModelChecker mc = VerifiersFactory.eINSTANCE.createModelCheckerImpl(); 
 mc.setUp(r);
 // use case 1
 VerificationResult result = mc.checkVerificationUnit(vc);
 // ... or 
 // use case 2
 mc.addVerificationUnit(vc1);
 mc.addVerificationUnit(vc2);
 // ...
 mv.checkAll();
 ResultsCollection rc = mc.getResultsCollection();

    The setUp(org.eclipse.emf.ecore.resource.Resource) method records the Resource context and creates a ResultsCollection to record all results when invoked with checkAll().

    The following features are implemented:

    • Resource Context
    • Results
    • Verification Units
    • Viewpoint Collection
    • Component Collection

      • checkVerificationUnit

        public VerificationResult checkVerificationUnit(VerificationUnit verificationUnit)
        Performs model-checking. This consists of three steps:
        1. Prepare the input for the external model-checker from the given model and specification.
        2. Execute the external model-checker with the prepared input.
        3. Obtain and process the results generated by the external model-checker and turn them into a VerificationResult object.

        Subclasses should provide a concrete implementation of these steps in the following methods:

        1. prepareInput(org.osate.xtext.aadl2.agcl.analysis.verifiers.VerificationUnit)
        2. callExternal(org.osate.xtext.aadl2.agcl.analysis.verifiers.ModelCheckerInput)
        3. processOutput(org.osate.xtext.aadl2.agcl.analysis.verifiers.ModelCheckerOutput)
        Specified by:
        checkVerificationUnit in interface ModelChecker
        Parameters:
        verificationUnit - a VerificationUnit
        Returns:
        a VerificationResult
